 <paragraph index="92" node_type="writer">Exclusivity seeking : each consumer have different exclusivity preference. Consequently , for simulating as close to real world scenarios as possible, exclusivity preferences of consumers are sampled from uniform distribution with min of 0 and max of 1 :</paragraph>
 <paragraph index="94" node_type="writer"> </paragraph>
